title: GEAR.GUNS.Tank.Offensive-CODEX
description:
C O D E X
P R E S E N T S

GEARGUNS - Tank offensive (c) Alexey Glinskiy

Release Date :  09/2016              Protection
Discs        :  1                    Genre      : Action

In GEARGUNS - Tank Offensive you will find  many  different  levels
which you will to go through following the plot of the  game.  Each
level has an alternate version in the Survival Mode where  you will
have to defend the planet from an alien invasion.

For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/526250/

- Extract
- Burn or mount the .iso
- Run setup.exe and install
- Play

General Notes:
- Block the game's exe in your firewall to prevent the game from
trying to go online ..
- If you install games to your systemdrive, it may be necessary
to run this game with admin privileges instead
